bio: I am a member of a Chinese community that has been following the development of OP projects. Long-term participation in various activities of OP.
contributionDescription: Long-term hold a certain number of OP and participate in various main network ecological activities. Under my influence, many people have joined in and actively participated in the ecological construction and development of OP. I am very optimistic about the future development prospects of the OP project and will continue to make contributions to the development of the project in the future.
